      "writtenOn": "2010-11-15T11:11:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The name \"android_console_open\" nearly implies that this is a method on an \"AndroidConsole\" object, I would prefer if you use something like android_\u003cverb\u003e_\u003csubject\u003e instead since this is not the case, e.g. \"android_open_console_fd()\" or \"android_connect_to_console()\"",
